{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1000 Waves is a game about progression as the player's ultimate goal is to clear all 1000 waves and defeating the final boss. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Procedurally generated dungeons hinder the movement of the player as they must maneuver around and avoid hazardous obstacles that may appear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/procgen.png?t=1732230873\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Within the center of the arena powerups will spawn the will temporarily enhance the player. A vast amount of unique enemy types will be encountered as you make your way to the 1000th wave. Utilize an array of unique weapons where some are more beneficial than others towards defeating certain enemy types.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/powerupspawning.png?t=1732230873\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every 25th wave you will encounter a tail pickup necessary for utilizing the bomb function and can be useful towards blocking enemy bullets and swiping away enemy swarms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/tailpickup.png?t=1732230873\" /></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additionally 0-3 perks have a chance at spawning that will boost many aspects of one's playthrough such as stronger bombs and enhancing powerup abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/perkexam.png?t=1732230873\" /></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience points are gathered via destroying enemies, collecting multiplier gems, and completing objectives within a certain amount of time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/multigemcluster.png?t=1732230873\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A few objectives include but are not limited to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pathway - Following a defined number of points, reaching 0 completes the objective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/pathway.png?t=1732230873\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defend - Destroy surrounding enemies before they collide with the objective, when the timer runs out it completes the objective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/defend.png?t=1732230873\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maneuver - Collect a defined number of orbs scattered around the arena before time runs out, once they have all been brought to the main objective it will be completed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/maneuver.png?t=1732230873\" /></p></li></ul></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience points gained can  be used to level up your ship in many ways such as increased firepower, heightened defense capabilities, and powerup longevity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/levelupsec.png?t=1732230873\" /></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"10K Multiplier","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3312510/5348727815a57006fdc93f17f9e69b984fe6b9cd.jpg"},{"name":"50K Multiplier","